  "detailed_description": "<h1>REVIEWS</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Inner Ashes is a showcase of talent in all its aspects. Its graphics are beautiful, as is its music and the symbolism it employs in its worlds. The sensitivity of its story and dialogue also do a great job of connecting with the emotions of anyone, whether they have experienced the disease or not.\" - 7/10 IGN Spain</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"It's a memorable game that will take you on an emotional journey. The story of Henry and Enid is engaging and will drive you to play until the very end, and the gameplay will challenge you. Every element of the game came together to tell a moving story and also show what it's like to live with Alzheimer's. Inner Ashes is certainly one of those games you should consider playing.\" - 7.5/10 KeenGamer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"With a graphic display, especially in the dreamlike scenarios, a superb artistic design that reflects a mind that is losing its memories. As for the sound, we again feel the love and care in this title, with an excellent Spanish dubbing, which conveys emotions in each of the voice actors and all emphasised by melodies and themes that pierce your heart, especially in certain moments.\" - 7/10 Comuesp</p></p><br><h1>WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.poster.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/f29a07b9c20caf66ed7a88e27bb93767.webm?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/f503f987992d8ec614736553a91bc1b8.poster.avif?t=1750430781\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/f503f987992d8ec614736553a91bc1b8.webm?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/7bee3292048f83ad0aaf641fbad4df4c.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br>Inner Ashes is a first-person narrative adventure in which the player experiences how Alzheimer’s affects people and their memories through an emotive story of a father and daughter set in dreamlike sequences.<br><br>The main character, Henry, must go on an introspective journey through two different realities on his quest to remember why he and his only daughter, Enid, have been estranged for so long.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/abdc630a8ad6a8bf678bd346c8ab7354.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br>Explore Henry's mind manifested as several dreamlike islands that represent different symptoms of Alzheimer’s, and unlock his memories by solving puzzles.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/f613ca044e1a60e194e29662982fe8cb.poster.avif?t=1750430781\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/f613ca044e1a60e194e29662982fe8cb.webm?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/f613ca044e1a60e194e29662982fe8cb.mp4?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/128ecaff4ff2b614cd89f5411b662c50.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br>Find out the truth about Henry and Enid by collecting the fragments of their past.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/6068d4dae577fd9548b46fef70404218.poster.avif?t=1750430781\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/6068d4dae577fd9548b46fef70404218.webm?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/6068d4dae577fd9548b46fef70404218.mp4?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/1c4228ceae37fcfd9be0b72c9ac80083.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br>Experience the daily life of an Alzheimer's patient and confront their day-to-day struggles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/05805c78ab59d03c6a1dfe7dcf7d458b.poster.avif?t=1750430781\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/05805c78ab59d03c6a1dfe7dcf7d458b.webm?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/05805c78ab59d03c6a1dfe7dcf7d458b.mp4?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/382040ee1d985d6b32089b093cbd65dd.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/5996fd404553b8c66bd30929f1901fea.avif?t=1750430781\" width=708 height=988 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/953706538977be66916908535fbb5328.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br><br>The mechanics of this game are based on the techniques used to help Alzheimer’s patients alleviate the symptoms of the disease.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Post-it notes help Henry to recognize items and remember how to use them.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/251ad1dc8b2de88d15cd33d06bd20331.poster.avif?t=1750430781\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/251ad1dc8b2de88d15cd33d06bd20331.webm?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/251ad1dc8b2de88d15cd33d06bd20331.mp4?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tangram puzzles stimulate Henry's memory and unlock important recollections of his life with Enid.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/3e0f42da4669926780a72b60484a7524.poster.avif?t=1750430781\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/3e0f42da4669926780a72b60484a7524.webm?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/3e0f42da4669926780a72b60484a7524.mp4?t=1750430781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755340/extras/a3ab2d7293a27d132323b8b71a6abdc4.avif?t=1750430781\" width=616 height=150 /></span>",
